      "title": "Sajith withdraws from the presidential race",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sajith Premadama, the leader of the Samagi Jana Balawegaye and the leader of the opposition, has decided not to participate in the vote to be held in the Parliament for the currently vacant presidency of Sri Lanka.",
        "Accordingly, Samagi Jana Balawegaya has decided to support Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma."
      ],
